text: Secretary of State Clinton visits Burma, making this the first visit by a chief US diplomat in over 50 years.
Authorities crack down on Occupy Wall Street protesters in Philadelphia and Los Angeles.
US Border Patrol agents arrest 14 suspected illegal immigrants as their boat nears the California coast.
A 30 minute police chase ends in Los Angeles after the suspect crashes into a parked car and flees on foot.
By a score of 85 to 63, Ohio State University gives Duke University its first loss of the season.
